    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving masterpiece utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver 333 hp with a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventative maintenance has been executed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate known chassis fatigue. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings, maintaining the car's celebrated torsional rigidity and turn-in precision. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is robust, exhibiting excellent compression and a clean oil analysis. A true driver\u2019s specimen optimized for performance over concours shelf-presence.",
