      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Audi S5 Sportback in sophisticated Daytona Gray Pearl. This vehicle strikes a perfect balance between executive luxury and exhilarating performance. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, with only minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014imperfections that do not detract from its striking curb appeal. Inside, the Magma Red fine Nappa leather interior is in excellent shape, free of tears or odors, showing only light softening of the driver\u2019s side bolsters. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the Audi Virtual Cockpit and premium Bang & Olufsen 3D sound system, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the 3.0L turbocharged V6 runs smoothly, backed by a complete dealership service history. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service and a multi-point inspection, ensuring the car is road-ready. The tires offer deep tread, and the brakes provide firm, responsive stopping power. This is a clean, honest example of a modern performance classic.",
      "price": 34500.0,
