      "description": "Offering a 2013 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit utilizes a 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission for lightning-fast gear synchronization and features the M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral traction. The chassis is dialed in with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing precise damping adjustments across varying road surfaces. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing, ensuring the longevity of the 8,400 RPM valvetrain. A driver-focused example with a clean subframe and robust induction system, ready for the enthusiast who demands linear power delivery.",
